--- infra [shared,critical] ---
DB        [R#*]  : PostgreSQL for persistent data (messages, channels, users) | AllRepos → THIS
Cache     [R#*]  : Valkey for ephemeral state (presence, typing, recent messages) | Sers → THIS
---

--- gateway [connection-lifecycle] ---
GateConn     [G#!$] : WS handshake, JWT auth, heartbeat | Clients ↔ THIS
GateRooms    [G#]   : Join/leave, member tracking, broadcast | GateConn ← THIS ↔ $pubsub
GatePresence [G#~]  : Online/offline/typing (ephemeral) | GateConn ← THIS ↔ $cache
---
